Let them see everything is okay.

1005
01:31:56,055 --> 01:31:58,889
Then stay in the kitchen
until I say to come out.

1006
01:31:59,558 --> 01:32:03,685
Then if they get trigger-happy,
you'll be out of the line of fire.

1007
01:32:06,606 --> 01:32:08,183
Then you'll let me go?

1008
01:32:15,698 --> 01:32:16,979
I'll let you go.

1009
01:32:31,047 --> 01:32:33,039
Is that the road you took?

1010
01:32:51,650 --> 01:32:55,019
Don't go in there fucking around.
In and out. You got me?

1011
01:32:55,153 --> 01:32:57,478
What do you think I'd do? Don't worry.

1012
01:33:13,463 --> 01:33:15,751
You sure this is it?

1013
01:33:17,758 --> 01:33:18,837
Yeah.

1014
01:35:13,244 --> 01:35:15,533
You got it straight?

1015
01:35:27,717 --> 01:35:28,748
Hi, baby.

1016
01:35:31,470 --> 01:35:33,262
Come on, Fantasia, let's go.

1017
01:35:33,389 --> 01:35:36,176
It'll be a few minutes.
I have to pack my stuff.

1018
01:35:37,685 --> 01:35:40,555
What stuff? All you had was your purse.

1019
01:35:41,021 --> 01:35:42,978
It won't be long. Come on in.

1020
01:35:43,189 --> 01:35:44,186
Shit!

1021
01:35:45,568 --> 01:35:46,731
I'll be back.

1022
01:35:46,861 --> 01:35:50,229
That's bullshit. I'm sticking on your ass.

1023
01:35:56,537 --> 01:35:58,909
She better not have bought any clothes.

1024
01:36:00,833 --> 01:36:02,624
What does she have to pack?

1025
01:36:02,918 --> 01:36:04,661
-Come on.
-Be careful. I love you.

1026
01:36:04,794 --> 01:36:06,916
Did you spend any of my money?

1027
01:36:10,842 --> 01:36:14,376
Fantasia? Where did she go?

1028
01:36:14,554 --> 01:36:19,014
Police officers, freeze!
Hands up or I'll blow you to fucking hell!

1029
01:36:19,225 --> 01:36:22,595
-What the fuck?
-Get on the floor! Now!

1030
01:36:22,729 --> 01:36:24,271
Who the fuck are you?

1031
01:36:25,063 --> 01:36:26,937
-You bitch!
-Shut up! Shut up!

1032
01:36:27,066 --> 01:36:29,817
-Why the fuck did you do this?
-I'm sorry.

1033
01:36:30,111 --> 01:36:31,189
Stay back!

1034
01:38:19,633 --> 01:38:20,629
210.

1035
01:38:23,387 --> 01:38:27,764
210, A-1 channel 1. Come in, goddamn it.
Hurry up.

1036
01:38:28,099 --> 01:38:30,554
Hurricane, where the hell have you been?

1037
01:38:31,228 --> 01:38:32,888
I need help out here.

1038
01:38:33,314 --> 01:38:34,723
What's your 10-20?

1039
01:38:35,690 --> 01:38:36,722
Oh, God.

1040
01:38:36,982 --> 01:38:39,474
Dale, what's your 20? Where are you?

1041
01:38:39,777 --> 01:38:44,440
I'm off the highway,
two miles down Sulphur Springs road.

1042
01:38:45,199 --> 01:38:49,493
There's a house.
In the woods, there's this house--

1043
01:38:49,954 --> 01:38:51,448
Is there an address?

1044
01:38:51,580 --> 01:38:56,823
I don't know the goddamn address.
Just send some help. And an ambulance.

1045
01:38:57,587 --> 01:39:01,037
I got three suspects down
and I'm hurtpretty bad.

1046
01:39:01,299 --> 01:39:05,295
-Three suspects down.
-You know Sulphur Springs Road?

1047
01:39:06,386 --> 01:39:07,631
Hold on, Byron.

1048
01:39:29,158 --> 01:39:30,403
Charlie, do something.

1049
01:39:30,535 --> 01:39:33,904
Dud, come on! Charlie's taking care of it.
Come on!

1050
01:40:03,275 --> 01:40:05,313
That son of a bitch nailed them.

1051
01:40:17,955 --> 01:40:18,952
Hey, man.

1052
01:40:20,499 --> 01:40:24,960
The ambulance is on the way.
I'll get you some blankets, okay?

1053
01:40:40,393 --> 01:40:41,936
Are you dead, mister?

1054
01:40:42,729 --> 01:40:44,272
Are you dead, mister?

1055
01:40:48,527 --> 01:40:50,685
-No, not quite.
-Where's the lady at?

1056
01:40:52,071 --> 01:40:53,447
She's over there.

1057
01:40:53,823 --> 01:40:57,274
Don't go away. Come back.
Come stay with me.

1058
01:41:04,959 --> 01:41:08,126
-Stay here with me.
-How did you get blood on yourself?

1059
01:41:09,464 --> 01:41:10,839
I got in a fight.

1060
01:41:13,967 --> 01:41:16,423
What do you do with your keys?

1061
01:41:19,765 --> 01:41:21,841
I lock things up.

1062
01:41:23,101 --> 01:41:25,391
Come here. I can't see your face.

1063
01:41:26,771 --> 01:41:28,811
Come a little closer.

1064
01:41:32,153 --> 01:41:33,315
Your name...

1065
01:41:34,862 --> 01:41:36,025
...is Byron.

1066
01:41:39,033 --> 01:41:40,776
You're five years old.

1067
01:41:42,454 --> 01:41:43,652
Four or five?

1068
01:41:44,039 --> 01:41:45,034
Five.

1069
01:41:47,500 --> 01:41:49,078
Just come sit with me.

